The state-transition audit found another concrete overclaim: the table says it covers every Boolean edge, but it omits several recovery/edge cases once the machine is in WARNING/ESCALATED/LATCHED-SAFE. I’m also validating the 4-second silence behavior against ArduPilot’s own documentation/source semantics, because that point cannot safely rest on the report’s disposition.
